list.name: Default
list.comment: More work to fully Mavenize the project. Moved the files to the resources directories. Tests include more account numbers, and missing file. Also including the entire .idea directory.

MESSAGE.value: Added test to parse all digits.
Added method to return an OCR Character based on the digit passed in. Added a test that currently fails.
Made ocrAccountString() an array instead of a concatenated number. The test still does not pass. Also did some minor reformatting.
Added code to ParseAccountNumber() so TestParseAccountNumber() now works correctly.
Added stub method to read the OCR file. Added a test that currently fails for that method. Also did some minor reformatting.
Added empty OCRFile.txt. Modified to test if the file can be opened.
Modified test to verify we read something from the file. Modified code to read the file.

Added OCR data to OCRFile.txt. Added TestReadOCRData() to test reading data from the file. Introduced SetUp test methods to reduce code duplication. Added a message in case of "File not found" exception.
Performed some refactoring due to inconsistent naming. Cleaned up some code. Removed 10th OCR Digit from OCRFile.txt since it is supposed to be a 9-digit account number.
Added test that currently fails to parse the data read from the file into an account number.
Added code to ParseString(). Test now works.

Reworked to get a list of strings from the file to handle multiple account numbers and reworked tests to test multiple account numbers. Streamlined ReadFile(). Moved ParseString() to AccountParser where it belongs and moved the test. This meant _ReadOCRFile could be made local. Added OCRConvert as an application. This completes User Story 1.
Started User Story 2. Added TestIsValidAccountNumber(). Test currently fails.

Finished User Story 2. Added code to IsValidAccountNumber() to calculate the checksum. TestIsValidAccountNumber() now succeeds. Split that test valid and invalid cases. Also added a second test to validate a different account number. Modified OCRConvert main to call IsValidAccountNumber() on the parsed account number. Modified ReadFile() to always pad the line read out to 27 characters. This was necessary to get around the editor stripping of trailing whitespace. Added additional account number to OCRFile2.txt.
More work to fully Mavenize the project. Also including the entire .idea directory.
